<h1 id="controlling-layout">Controlling Layout</h1>
<p>The following properties can be used to control the layout of a RichString:</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="./ref/Topten.RichTextKit.RichString.MaxWidth">Topten.RichTextKit.RichString.MaxWidth</a></li>
<li><a href="./ref/Topten.RichTextKit.RichString.MaxHeight">Topten.RichTextKit.RichString.MaxHeight</a></li>
<li><a href="./ref/Topten.RichTextKit.RichString.MaxLines">Topten.RichTextKit.RichString.MaxLines</a></li>
<li><a href="./ref/Topten.RichTextKit.RichString.DefaultAlignment">Topten.RichTextKit.RichString.DefaultAlignment</a></li>
<li><a href="./ref/Topten.RichTextKit.RichString.DefaultDirection">Topten.RichTextKit.RichString.DefaultDirection</a></li>
</ul>
<p>Per-paragraph control of layout is available through the following
